{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_06_02",
  "title": "miho 2話 寂しいとしか言いようがない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、ブライダル情報誌の\nウエディングドレスの着用モデルを私にやってほしいと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ you want me\nto model a wedding dress for a bridal magazine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "話は分かりましたけど……モデルというなら\nそれこそ、元本職のfranとkanaが適任では？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand what you’re saying‚ but… If it’s for a model‚\nwouldn’t Fran and Kana be more suitable?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7666416168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "先方も当然、それは検討したらしいんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course they considered that‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8659409841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "franさんは今回のコンセプトと少し異なり\nkanaさんも……やや若く見えてしまうと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san differs slightly from this concept\nand Kana-san… would look too young.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "これから結婚する人向けの宣伝記事な訳ですから\n読者とかけ離れていては、意味がないということですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's an advertisement for people about to get married‚\nso it would be meaningless if the model is too different from the readers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました\n詳細とスケジュールを共有しておいて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I understand.\nPlease share the details and schedule with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですか！？　……その、mihoさん\n結婚とかにはまるで興味なさそうでしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that okay!? …Um‚ Miho-san‚\nyou didn’t seem interested in marriage or anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1330325422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そう言えば前にそんな話をしましたっけ\nですが仕事なら、断る理由は特にありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ right‚ we did talk about that before.\nBut if it’s work‚ I have no particular reason to refuse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんが仕事の選り好みをする訳ないですよね\nいやぁ……良かった、怒られるかと心配で心配で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew Miho-san wouldn't be picky about her work.\nWhew… I’m so relieved. I was worried you’d be angry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "怒りはしませんよ\nもっといい仕事を取ってこいとは常々思っていますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't get angry.\nThough I always think that you should bring me better jobs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3108178937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、善処します……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I'll do my best…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8729293983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "それと……このくらいで私が怒ると面白がっていた\nあの二人も、お仕置きしてやらないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… those two‚ who were amused that I would get angry\nwith this‚ need to be punished.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8000040691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、ほどほどにお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P-Please go easy on them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4432243109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影当日、スタジオ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― The day of the shoot‚ at the studio",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.108689205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.4486891669
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.5420240642
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "ⅢXのmihoです\n今日はよろしくお願いいたします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m miho from IIIX.\nPlease take care of me today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5333374024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7056747359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "ドレスがよく似合ってる？\n……ふふ、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The dress suits me well?\n…Fufu‚ thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0666707357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.9343367657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "ブランドからお借りした最高級のドレスですし\n綺麗に映るように、精一杯頑張らせていただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a top-quality dress borrowed from the brand‚\nso I'll do my best to look beautiful in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2666707357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.0941326858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは、ファンの人達と\n結婚しているようなものですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idols are like\nmarried to their fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1287645512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "カメラの向こうに大切なパートナーがいると思って\n今日はやらせていただきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll do this shoot today as if my precious partner\nis on the other side of the camera.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6655610242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.8482822181
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（さすが、あれなら誰が見ても『幸せな花嫁』だ）\n（これなら撮影は問題なく終わりそうだけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（As expected‚ anyone would see her as a \"happy bride\".）\n（It looks like the shoot will go smoothly‚ but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6333374024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.1758786282
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.1758786282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2258786282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。いやぁ、バッチリでしたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. Well‚ that was perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.0953374864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.1526842278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1526842278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "か、カメラ前とは全然雰囲気違いますね\n……やっぱりこの仕事、気乗りしませんでしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-your atmosphere is completely different from in front of the camera.\n…You weren't really into this job‚ were you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.0333343507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.8725416345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "たとえ興味がなかろうと、本番では顔には出しませんし\n仕事はきちんと完遂しますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if I'm not interested‚ I don't show it during the shoot‚\nand I always complete my work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3000010174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.8195934774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのそのプロ意識は、俺も信頼してます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I trust IIIX's professionalism.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8195934774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今日はやけにため息ばかりついてますけど\nそれはウエディングには興味ないからですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you’ve been sighing a lot today.\nIs it because you're not interested in weddings…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.7000010174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.1440378828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
