      "text": "言いたくないから黙ってるのに\nそれをあえて聞くというのは、どんな神経なんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm staying silent because I don't want to talk about it‚\nand you dare ask me about it? What are you thinking?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.6000010174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry…",
        "id": ""
