      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね！？\n少し調べてはいたんですが、勉強不足でした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have!?\nI did a little research‚ but it wasn't enough…",
        "id": ""
