      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_02-mhk021.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、私は結婚のイメージも持てませんでしたから\n友人が結婚したら、グループはどうしようとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I never really thought about getting married‚ so…\n\"What would happen to the group if my friend got married\"‚ or…",
        "id": ""
